{"word":"G2046 - ἐρέω - eréō - er-eh'-o - Call","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், பேசு, கேள்"},{"paragraph":"call, say, speak, tell"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably a fuller form of <a href=\"#/G4483 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o/4483\">G4483</a>; an alternate for <a href=\"#/G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o/2036\">G2036</a> in certain tenses; to <i>utter</i>, that is, <i>speak</i> or <i>say:</i> - call, say, speak (of), tell.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}